{"tid":2329561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"滙豐PayMe接入順豐香港　實現BBIWU","createTime":"2020-12-17T09:54:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T16:38:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7be4ccbd3aaf863e455c35f8eda1e7e41457c69c","tid":2329561,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:54:11.000Z","msg":"滙豐旗下個人對商戶(P2M)支付方案PayMe for Business的商戶網絡進一步擴展，最新有順豐速運(香港)加入。<br />\n<br />\n用戶現已可於任何地方使用順豐香港上門收派服務，或於遍布全港約120個順豐香港網點，以PayMe，即無現金支付。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐PayMe主管黃朱寶燕表示，歡迎順豐香港加入PayMe for Business的商戶網絡。PayMe現擴展至物流服務行業，支持與日俱增的無現金化支付交易。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on. cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201217/bkn-20201217174216613-1217_00842_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"3153df7a4b0453ec7fdc04871f68074ab1b1c39b","tid":2329561,"uid":41368,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:55:07.000Z","msg":"hsbc : 我凍結你個郵件"},{"pid":"9aaf710771a4f1104831270a7bb8cbfc95602655","tid":2329561,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3153df7a4b0453ec7fdc04871f68074ab1b1c39b","tid":2329561,"uid":41368,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:55:07.000Z","msg":"hsbc : 我凍結你個郵件"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d3893bdbab5ca88c0005fecb44bbc8cfe61613","tid":2329561,"uid":124372,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"匯豐同順豐合併<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0361bda3cc662a510e98a88150f28c4252f5ec4","tid":2329561,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:18:26.000Z","msg":"你的快件